condition.narrative: The Recipient shall, not later than 60 days after the Effective Date, update and adopt, in form and substance acceptable to theAssociation and following the guidelines set forth in the Project Implementation Manual, a grievance redress mechanism thatencompasses transparent, timely and fair procedures that will allow people potentially affected by the Project to peacefully settleany possible grievance and will ensure that all complaints received from Beneficiaries and other interested stakeholders related toany activity under the Project, are properly and timely addressed.
